Description: Provides selected image-related C/C++ header files from the
    'stb' single-file libraries for use by R packages through the
    'LinkingTo' field. Included headers provide image loading, image writing,
    and image resizing functionality. The package elects the MIT license
    alternative offered by the upstream headers.
